          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Slide 5: People Making a Pachamanca -->
      <div class="slide">
        <h2 class="slide-title">People Making a Pachamanca</h2>
        <div class="slide-content">
          <p>Pachamanca is a communal cooking tradition that brings people together. Preparing and sharing this traditional meal strengthens community bonds and preserves indigenous cultural practices.</p>
